headline: Dollar General Delivery Push Reaches 17,000 Stores As Valuation Debated
summary: Dollar General has expanded its myDG Delivery same day service to over 17,000 locations across the United States. The rollout focuses on improving access for underserved and rural communities that may have limited retail and delivery options. The move builds on Dollar General's broader push into digital convenience and operational reach.
